# ### Welcome to the Ocean
This place is filled with fishes, and feesh, and other marine life that my or may not exist. Coral, sand, and rocks are also included in this amazing place.

### Fish
Fish are reptiles that live in the ocean. Most fish don't have lungs, but some, such as the lungfish, have them.

### Feesh
Feesh are similar to fish, but have one key difference, their tail is only and outline, and they don't have gills. Nobody knows how the breathe, heck, nobody knows if they're real!

### Land
It is the land... what did you think it was?

### Support or Contact
If you can't breathe under water and don't know how to swim, call the coast guard.
